Interface IRepository<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of objects managed by the repository.
All Known Implementing Classes:
AppointmentRepository, InvoiceRepository, MedicineRepository, MedicineRequestRepository, NotificationRepository, PatientRepository, PrescriptionItemRepository, PrescriptionRepository, Repository, StaffRepository, UnavailableDateRepository
public interface IRepository<T>
Interface for a generic repository to manage storage and retrieval of objects.
